    },
    {
      "text": "Argus is a 1986 vertically scrolling shooter video game developed by NMK and published by Jaleco for Japanese arcades. A port to the Famicom was released the same year. An emulated version of the original arcade game is included as part of their Arcade Archives series by Hamster Corporation for the Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4 on August 30, 2018, as the game's first release outside Japan.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "『アーガス』（Argus）は日本マイコン開発が開発し、1986年1月にジャレコが発売した業務用ビデオゲーム。宇宙戦争を題材にした縦スクロールシューティングゲームである。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "wikipedia_ja"
    },
    {
      "text": "Argus (アーガス?, Āgasu) è un videogioco arcade sparatutto a scorrimento del 1986 pubblicato da Jaleco. Ne uscì una conversione per Nintendo Entertainment System, poi inclusa anche nella raccolta Jaleco Collection Vol. 1 per PlayStation. Nel 2018 il titolo emulato è stato distribuito da Hamster Corporation per Nintendo Switch e PlayStation 4.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    }
